'''Merchant Row''' was an area located aboard [[Outland Transit Station]], a large [[Space station/Legends|space station]]<ref name="BountyHunter" /> in the [[Baxel sector/Legends|Baxel sector]] of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy's]] [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]].<ref name="TEA">''[[The Essential Atlas]]''</ref> Made up of a number of crowded streets and alleyways, Merchant Row was home to various [[Merchant/Legends|salespeople]] attempting to sell their wares to potential customers.<ref name="BountyHunter" />

==Behind the scenes==
Outland Transit Station's Merchant Row was first introduced to the ''[[Star Wars]]'' universe in the [[2002]] ''[[Star Wars: Bounty Hunter]]'' [[Star Wars video games|video game]], developed and published by [[LucasArts]].<ref name="BountyHunter" /> The area later received an informational entry in the [[2008]] reference guide ''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''.<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>

